title: Fixed bug in loading calendar
message:
Fixed bug in loading calendar

In next scenario, the calendar was loaded but not shown:
- open app, select address
- close app
- open app, go to settings - address
- don't chose an address, but go back
- calendar is not shown

title: don't check modifications date automaticly (closes #27)
message:
don't check modifications date automaticly (closes #27)

It's not necessary to automaticly check the last modifications date of the open-data each time the app opens. The user can still re-download the data by pressing the Refresh-button.
